sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant ING as Ingestion Lambda
    participant DDB as DynamoDB
    participant EB as EventBridge
    participant VAL as Validation Lambda
    participant ENR as Enrichment Lambda
    participant COMP as Completion Lambda

    Note over C,COMP: Synchronous path
    C->>API: POST /orders {tenantId, customer, items, idempotencyKey}
    API->>ING: Lambda invoke (sync)
    ING->>DDB: Query GSI2: idempotencyKey exists?
    DDB-->>ING: null (new order)
    ING->>DDB: PutItem (status='received', ConditionalExpression: pk NOT EXISTS)
    ING->>EB: PutEvents: order.received
    ING-->>API: 201 {order}
    API-->>C: 200 OK (~100ms)

    Note over C,COMP: Asynchronous processing
    EB->>VAL: SQS trigger: order.received event
    VAL->>DDB: GetItem: order
    VAL->>DDB: UpdateItem: status='validated'
    VAL->>EB: PutEvents: order.validated
    VAL-->>EB: done

    EB->>ENR: SQS trigger: order.validated event
    ENR->>DDB: GetItem: order
    ENR->>DDB: UpdateItem: status='enriched' + enriched lineItems
    ENR->>EB: PutEvents: order.enriched
    ENR-->>EB: done

    EB->>COMP: SQS trigger: order.enriched event
    COMP->>DDB: GetItem: order
    COMP->>DDB: UpdateItem: status='completed'
    COMP->>EB: PutEvents: order.completed
    COMP-->>EB: done

    Note over C,COMP: Full round-trip typically < 10 seconds
